courses.feedback_evaluation:
1. Send email to the teacher, give him/her a call, or come to his/her office, especially for issues that require immediate action;
2. Express your views in the mid-term and term-end course evaluation;
3. Express your views (or ask a student representative to help you convey the messages) in the staff-student consultation meeting held every year;
4. Post a message on the forum of the course website or on the Discussion board of the CUHK Blackboard.

